HEADWORD: millrace
<hw>millrace</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a channel from a millpond to a
millwheel, to provide the water current that turns the
millwheel.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> millrun.</syn>⟦br⟧
